text: Turck is a small unincorporated community located within Cherokee County, Kansas, United States. Its elevation is 932 feet. ==History== Turck had a post office from 1889 until 1891. ==References== ==Further reading== * History of Cherokee County, Kansas; Nathanial Allison; Biographical Publishing; 646 pages; 1904.
